textfsm_template:
Value DEVICE_ID (\S+)
Value LOCAL_INTF (\S+ \d+/\d+)
Value HOLDTIME (\d+)
Value CAPABILITY (\S+)
Value PLATFORM (\S+)
Value PORT_ID (\S+ \d+/\d+)

Start
  ^Device\sID.*Local\sIntrfce.*Holdtme.*Capability.*Platform.*Port\sID\s*$$
